Text: Lets talk about your home loanJerry Thank you for requesting more information from Quicken Loans through our website We are excited to have this chance to demonstrate our worldclass customer service to you I made an initial attempt to contact you to gather the additional information required to process your application but have not been able to get through Please reply to this message with the best time to call and the phone number you would like me to use If it is more convenient you can also call me direct at Ext Our phone lines are open MondayThursday am pm Friday am pm and Saturday am pm all times Eastern If I am not available one of the other loan consultants on my team will be happy to assist you Interest rates change daily For the latest rates on our many programs you can call anytime I look forward to working with you to complete your application Sincerely Daniel Jenuwine Mortgage Banker Phone Ext Email

Thank you for selecting QuickenLoansJerry Thank you for submitting your loan information to QuickenLoans All of the information you provided will be kept strictly confidential My name is Daniel Jenuwine and I have been assigned to be your personal Mortgage Banker Your application number is Please keep this number handy when corresponding with us regarding your loan application So what happens next I will be contacting you within hours to introduce myself and review your information with you Your application will then be submitted to our RocketLoan system for a quick approval I will request the documentation required to meet the conditions of your approval We will deliver your loan package containing your application and written confirmation of your loan terms to you within hours If you have any questions please email me at or call and ask for Daniel Jenuwine Hours of operation for our QuickenLoans Customer Service Center are am pmEST MondayThursday am pmEST Friday and am pmEST Saturday All applications submitted after hours will be handled the next working business day Have a great day Daniel Jenuwine Quicken Loans Phone Extension Email
